{"tid":2105664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚廁所板 見你縮左咁耐 都仲未回應梁頌恆點樣搞衰獨派","createTime":"2020-07-12T19:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T20:08:33.000Z","uid":15787,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"60981132f21dfb38ab7bebf210afe8a6807734db","tid":2105664,"uid":15787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T19:43:28.000Z","msg":"見今既咁多鄒家成支持者 絕對唔會唔識人稱廁所板<br />\n即係早前係連登開post直呼自己何梓聰個位<br />\n<br />\n專登開post屌梁頌恆唔好再做柒事 <br />\n又屈人地坐的士走個位<br />\n<br />\n或者無咩人睇過個個post 為免大家要再搵post<br />\n已經cap圖俾大家睇 咁難得鄒家成支持者上哂線<br />\n<br />\n咁真係要講下屌同路人係咩玩法<br />\n<br />\n我就絕對認同民主黨同泛民唔係同路人 <br />\n要屌佢絕對理所當然<br />\n<br />\n但點解何梓聰會屌梁頌恆 你地又唔會開口屌鳩佢<br />\n話哂同路人 屌完就不負責任走左去<br />\n一句道歉一句解釋都冇 咁都幾雙重標準 <br />\n鄒生支持者仲好意思屌話鄒家成係潑婦個位樓主<br />\n<br />\n想問下鄒生支持者點睇件事 見你地咁齊人<br />\n頭先又咁積極 咁屌何梓聰應該都不遺餘力啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDY3oXh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDY3oXh.png&h=f730750c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7urc1JZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7urc1JZ.png&h=48cffde6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FC366aH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFC366aH.png&h=e6fa268f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcf078a7d72aee7ab0866798efb66b4efe351d9d","tid":2105664,"uid":22692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T19:48:01.000Z","msg":"佢搞柒係事實"},{"pid":"d2bdb2a9a5e7668cb47a098a409bc6918d3028d9","tid":2105664,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T19:56:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eb597586558c1a70699c335fdcb063ed21ff06c","tid":2105664,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T19:56:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bbfd112331922cccb88cdbe3e258a9a55f2886c","tid":2105664,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5a7